org.jhove2.app.util.documenter
Class FormatModuleDocumenter

java.lang.Object
  org.jhove2.app.util.documenter.FormatModuleDocumenter
All Implemented Interfaces:
ModuleDocumenter
public class FormatModuleDocumenter
extends Object
implements ModuleDocumenter

Intended to collection information about FormatModule, its Format, any Profiles and Profile Formats, any specifications associated with the format, and the Reportable properties of the FormatModule. The latter comes from static analysis of the Java class; other information comes for the Spring Bean in the JHOVE2 configuration files

Author:
smorrissey
